**Event Information:**

- **Event Name:** SAINTCON 2024
- **Date of Registration Opening:** July 15, 2024, 12:01 PM MDT
- **Registration Link:** [Register for SAINTCON 2024](https://register.saintcon.org/)

**Pricing for Event Passes:**
1. **Standard Conference Pass (No Meals Provided)**
   - **Cost:** $290
   - **Includes:**
     - Electronic Badge
     - 4 Days of Content
     - Access to Presentations, Events, Contests, Communities, and Expo Floor
     - All-Day Drinks Included

2. **Standard Conference Pass (Includes Meals)**
   - **Cost:** $390
   - **Includes:**
     - Electronic Badge
     - 4 Days of Content
     - Access to Presentations, Events, Contests, Communities, and Expo Floor
     - All-Day Drinks Included
     - Lunches (requires meal-card at check-in)

3. **Standard Conference Pass (Community Supporter)**
   - **Cost:** $500
   - **Includes:**
     - Electronic Badge
     - 4 Days of Content
     - Access to Presentations, Events, Contests, Communities, and Expo Floor
     - All-Day Drinks Included
     - Lunches (requires meal-card at check-in)
     - Community Support MiniBadge
     - Proceeds Support scholarship and student programs

**General Description:**
SAINTCON 2024 focuses on affordability for Cybersecurity and IT professionals despite rising costs. It promotes inclusivity within the cybersecurity community.

**Additional Links:**
- [More Details](https://saintcon.org/register/)
